Unikey (Vietnamese Input Method) engine support for Fcitx

Released under mixed GPLv2+

Dependencies:
- CMake >= 3.6
- ECM (Extra CMake Modules) >= 1.0.0
- Fcitx5 >= 5.1.13
- Gettext
- Qt6 (Core, Gui, Widgets) — optional, for macro/keymap editors
- Fcitx5Qt6WidgetsAddons >= 5.0.12 — optional, required if Qt is enabled

Build and install with Ninja (default, with Qt editors and tests):
$ cmake -B build -G Ninja -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
$ ninja -C build
# ninja -C build install

Build and install with Make:
$ cmake -B build -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
$ make -C build
# make -C build install

Minimal build (no Qt editors, no tests):
$ cmake -B build -G Ninja -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DENABLE_QT=Off -DENABLE_TEST=Off
$ ninja -C build
# ninja -C build install

Build with coverage:
$ cmake -B build -G Ninja -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DENABLE_COVERAGE=On
$ ninja -C build
$ ninja -C build coverage

CMake options:
  -DENABLE_QT=On/Off        Enable Qt based macro/keymap editor (default: On)
  -DENABLE_TEST=On/Off       Build tests (default: On)
  -DENABLE_COVERAGE=On/Off   Build with gcov coverage support (default: Off)

Run tests:
$ ctest --test-dir build

Uninstall:
$ ninja -C build uninstall
